---

<section id="a-savoir" class="info-section reveal">
	<div class="info-content">
		<div class="info-header">
			<svg class="info-icon" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
				<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" fill="#4f46e5"/>
				<circle cx="12" cy="8" r="1.35" fill="#ffffff"/>
				<path
					d="M12 11v6"
					fill="none"
					stroke="#ffffff"
					stroke-width="2"
					stroke-linecap="round"
				/>
			</svg>
			<h3>À savoir</h3>
		</div>
		<ul class="info-list">
			<li>
				<svg class="check-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
					<polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
				</svg>
				<span>Hors période du Festival d'Avignon, les logements sont destinés prioritairement à la location meublée sous bail étudiant ou bail mobilité.</span>
			</li>
			<li>
				<svg class="check-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
					<polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
				</svg>
				<span>Une caution émanant d'un tiers ou d'un organisme agréé (Visale, Garantme, Cautioneo) est nécessaire pour la constitution du dossier.</span>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.info-section {
		margin: 3rem 0;
		padding: 0;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a5b4fc 0%, #818cf8 35%, #c4b5fd 100%);
		border-radius: 16px;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.2);
	}

	.info-content {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2.5rem;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #fafbff 100%);
		margin: 2rem;
		border-radius: 14px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.35);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(67, 56, 202, 0.08);
	}

	.info-header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		padding-bottom: 1rem;
		border-bottom: 2px solid #e0e7ff;
	}

	.info-icon {
		flex-shrink: 0;
		filter: drop-shadow(0 3px 10px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.35));
	}

	.info-content h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin: 0;
		color: #1a1a1a;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.info-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.25rem;
	}

	.info-list li {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		gap: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #44403c;
		padding: 1rem;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f5f3ff 0%, #ffffff 60%);
		border-radius: 10px;
		border-left: 4px solid #6366f1;
		transition:
			transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1),
			background 0.35s ease,
			box-shadow 0.35s ease;
	}

	.info-list li:hover {
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ede9fe 0%, #faf5ff 100%);
		transform: translateX(10px) scale(1.01);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15);
	}

	.check-icon {
		color: #667eea;
		flex-shrink: 0;
		margin-top: 0.15rem;
	}

	.info-list li span {
		flex: 1;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.info-content {
			padding: 1.5rem;
			margin: 1rem;
		}

		.info-header {
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		}

		.info-content h3 {
			font-size: 1.25rem;
		}

		.info-list li {
			font-size: 0.95rem;
			padding: 0.875rem;
		}

		.check-icon {
			width: 18px;
			height: 18px;
		}

		.info-icon {
			width: 34px;
			height: 34px;
		}
	}
</style>

